snippet.title: GALAK-Z : The Void Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The ultimate 2D space combat simulator!  Brand New “The Void” DLC offers endless gameplay, Online Leaderboards, and a Daily Challenge that allows players to compete worldwide for the top score.
